  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The spec has updated to include more details about rewards, a PR dealing with this will add the following to the Casper Package\r\n-  `reward_quotient = BASE_REWARD_QUOTIENT * int(sqrt(total_deposits in ETH))`\r\n\r\nThe reward quotient will specify how the validator would be rewarded are and 1/`reward_quotient` would define the per slot maximum interest rate. \r\n \r\n-  `quadratic_penalty_quotient = int(sqrt(SQRT_E_DROP_TIME / SLOT_DURATION))`\r\n\r\nIf a validator is offline for N slots then the validator would be slashed this amount : (N^2/2)/ `quadratic_penalty_quotient`\r\n\r\n-   Adjust participating validator's balances as defined in the spec depending on if `time_since_finality <= 2 * CYCLE_LENGTH`",
